      • getStudents

        StudentList getStudents​(java.lang.String name,
                        int semester,
                        java.lang.String classLetters)
        Method that conducts a filter on list of student and return filtered list, criteria of filtering are passed as parameters and can be in any combination (e.g. filtering by semester and name at the same time). Method recognizes which parameters it should use in filtering based on their values.
        Parameters:
        name - name that filtered students should have
        semester - semester on which filtered students should be
        classLetters - class letters (e.g. DK) of class that filtered students should be part of
        Returns:
        StudentList containing students that match criteria of the filtering

      • getSessions

        SessionList getSessions​(Date date,
                        StudentClass studentClass,
                        java.lang.String nameOfTheRoom)
        Method conducting a search based on passed parameters (search can be done based on 1 parameter or combinations of 2 parameters or all 3 parameters). Method recognizes which based on which parameters it should conduct search and returns result of search. Purpose of this method is to filter data about session.
        Parameters:
        date - date on which sessions should happen
        studentClass - student class that should be participating in sessions
        nameOfTheRoom - name of the room in which session should take place
        Returns:
        SessionList containing sessions that match passed parameters

      • getAllAvailableRoomsOnDateAndTimeSlot

        RoomList getAllAvailableRoomsOnDateAndTimeSlot​(Date date,
                                               TimeSlot timeSlot)
        Method searching for rooms that are not reserved at given date and timeslot, the search is conducted with use of loops and with use of the property of the system that indexes of dates and timeslots that represent one reservation are the same
        Parameters:
        date - date at which rooms should be not reserved
        timeSlot - timeslot at which rooms should not be reserved
        Returns:
        RoomList containing only rooms that do not have reservation at given date and timeslot
